==Korean==
===Verb===
'''떼다'''  (''tteda'')
# To [[detach]], [[remove]], [[take off]]
# To [[separate]] 
# To [[unseal]]
# To [[wean]] 
# To [[deduct]]
# To [[reserve]], [[spare]], [[set aside]]  

====Synonyms====
*[[뜯다]] (''tteudda, tteutda'') cf. To [[tithe]]

====Derived terms====
*[[떼어내다]]  (''tteeonaeda'') To [[split]] [[off]], [[tear]] [[off]] 
*[[떼어먹다]]  (''tteeomeogda, -meokda'') To [[embezzle]], [[evade]] (''payment'')
*[[물어떼다]]  (''murEoTteda'') To [[bite]] [[off]] 
*[[잡아떼다]] (''jabATteda'') To [[split]]; [[deny]] (''suspicion'')
*'''떼어걷다'''  (''tteeogeodda, -geotda'') (''assumed'')  To [[collect]] (''what is [[set aside]], e.g., [[tenth]] or [[tithe]] from Old English [[teogothian]] "to tithe", [[teogotha]] "tenth, tithe"'')

